          Dog Sitting
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
          In-home care while you're away for work or vacation. Your pet is our
          priority.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 with animation -->
      <div
        class="bg-sky-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover-grow transition-all duration-300 transform hover:shadow-xl animate-slide-in-left animate-delay-200"
